    "(2) Homogeneous or Heterogeneous: Agents may have identical functions (homogeneous) or diverse functions and expertise (heterogeneous).Each LLM-based agent can be represented as a node 𝑣 𝑖 in a graph 𝐺 (𝑉, 𝐸), where edges 𝑒 𝑖,𝑗 ∈ 𝐸 represent interactions between agents 𝑣 𝑖 and 𝑣 𝑗.",
    "In this section, we review recent studies on LMA systems in software engineering, organizing these applications across various stages of the software development lifecycle, including requirements engineering, code generation, quality assurance, and software maintenance.",
